title: Lana Del Rey Playing Surprise SXSW Set Tomorrow
text: As rumored, Lana Del Rey is indeed playing a surprise set at SXSW tomorrow. Apple Music has already hosted shows with Vince Staples , Spoon, and the Chainsmokers, and tomorrow night, they're bringing Lana to their performance space at 612 W 4th Street. Badges or artist wristbands will be required to attend. More Â»
